item.title: Episode 813: Trump's Sinking Economy; Pritzker Calls for Trump Removal
item.description:
This week on Ring of Fire:

As Donald Trump prepares to lay off potentially thousands of government workers, the economy is already reeling from an unemployment crisis that is getting worse by the month. The jobs numbers for September from ADP have revealed that the country LOST nearly 40,000 jobs last month, the first time we’ve seen NEGATIVE growth since Donald Trump’s first term in office...
